Package PIM

Interface ServiceDependency

All Superinterfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
public interface ServiceDependency extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
A representation of the model object 'Service Dependency'.

The following features are supported:

  • Consumer Operation
  • Is Wrapped By Circuit Breaker
  • Provider Name
  • Provider Destination
  • Environment
  • Generating PSM
See Also:
  • PIMPackage.getServiceDependency()
